OL,5,G1900 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FIn a custom-built mobile surgery,
OL,7,     FGPs have a busy week helping
OL,8,     Fpatients including a boy with an
OL,9,     Finverted chest, a woman with a
OL,10,     Fmysterious rash, and an injury
OL,11,     Fcaused by a horse.
OL,12,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,14,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,15,     Funder the microscope. The hospital
OL,16,     Fis two porters down, marking a big
OL,17,     Fproblem for Sister Jane.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
