OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FTwo ladies keep Dr Dev Shah busy:
OL,7,     Fone has a large lipoma on her
OL,8,     Fback, the other a cyst on her
OL,9,     Fforehead. 19-year-old Abby hopes
OL,10,     FDr Natalia Spierings can rid her
OL,11,     Fof lumps on her ears.
OL,12,G0000 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,13,     FIn Orpington, a rescue team
OL,14,     Fbattles to save the life of an
OL,15,     Felderly motorist trapped in the
OL,16,     Fwreckage of his car. In Maidstone,
OL,17,     FParamedic Nathan provides urgent
OL,18,     Fcare at a hit and run.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
